   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "import json\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "import re\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "from tqdm import tqdm\n",
    "\n",
    "embedding_method = \"pool\"\n",
    "\n",
    "def parse_experiment_name(folder_name):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Extracts experiment parameters from folder name\"\"\"\n",
    "    # Pattern for parsing folder name\n",
    "    pattern = r'(\\d+_\\d+_\\d+_)?(\\w+)_ep(\\d+)_lr([\\d.e-]+)_bs(\\d+)_eval(\\d+)_seed(\\d+)(?:_(\\w+))?'\n",
    "    match = re.search(pattern, folder_name)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if match:\n",
    "        return {\n",
    "            'dataset_name': match.group(2),\n",
    "            'epochs': int(match.group(3)),\n",
    "            'lr': float(match.group(4)),\n",
    "            'batch_size': int(match.group(5)),\n",
    "            'eval_every': int(match.group(6)),\n",
    "            'seed': int(match.group(7)),\n",
    "            'use_qwen3': match.group(8) == 'qwen3' if match.group(8) else False,\n",
    "            'dataset_strategy': 'single',\n",
    "            'sampling_strategy': 'balanced',\n",
    "            'positive_ratio': 1.0\n",
    "        }\n",
    "    return {}\n",
    "\n",
    "def load_model_config(model_path):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Loads model config from checkpoint\"\"\"\n",
    "    try:\n",
            "        # Check if file exists\n",
    "        if not os.path.exists(model_path):\n",
    "            return None\n",
    "        \n",
            "        # Load checkpoint\n",
    "        try:\n",
    "            checkpoint = torch.load(model_path, map_location='cpu', weights_only=True)\n",
    "        except Exception:\n",
    "            checkpoint = torch.load(model_path, map_location='cpu', weights_only=False)\n",
    "        \n",
            "        # Extract config\n",
    "        config = checkpoint.get('config', {})\n",
    "        \n",
            "        # Ensure config is a dictionary\n",
    "        if not isinstance(config, dict):\n",
    "            if hasattr(config, 'to_dict'):\n",
    "                config = config.to_dict()\n",
    "            else:\n",
                    "                # If it's an object, convert its attributes to dictionary\n",
    "                config = {k: v for k, v in config.__dict__.items() \n",
    "                         if not k.startswith('_')}\n",
    "        \n",
    "        return config\n",
    "    except Exception as e:\n",
            "        print(f\"Error loading model config from {model_path}: {str(e)}\")\n",
    "        return None\n",
    "\n",
    "def find_best_model_path(folder_path):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Finds path to best model in experiment folder\"\"\"\n",
    "    # Check if best_models.json exists\n",
    "    best_models_file = os.path.join(folder_path, \"best_models.json\")\n",
    "    if not os.path.exists(best_models_file):\n",
    "        return None\n",
    "    \n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        with open(best_models_file, 'r') as f:\n",
    "            best_models_info = json.load(f)\n",
    "        \n",
            "        # Get best model information\n",
    "        best_model_info = best_models_info['best_models'][0]\n",
    "        model_path = best_model_info['model_path']\n",
    "        \n",
            "        # Check if model exists\n",
    "        if not os.path.exists(model_path):\n",
                "            # Try relative path\n",
    "            model_filename = best_model_info['model_filename']\n",
    "            model_path = os.path.join(folder_path, model_filename)\n",
    "            \n",
    "            if not os.path.exists(model_path):\n",
    "                return None\n",
    "        \n",
    "        return model_path\n",
    "    except Exception as e:\n",
            "        print(f\"Error finding best model: {str(e)}\")\n",
    "        return None\n",
    "\n",
    "# Path to results folder\n",
    "results_dir = f\"/home/jovyan/rahmatullaev/rand_exps/LLMs4OL-Challenge/src/taskC/method_v5_hm/results_{embedding_method}\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# List to store data from all experiments\n",
    "experiments_data = []\n",
    "\n",
    "# Iterate through all folders in results\n",
    "for folder_name in tqdm(os.listdir(results_dir)):\n",
    "    folder_path = os.path.join(results_dir, folder_name, \"best_models\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Check if it's a folder\n",
    "    if not os.path.isdir(folder_path):\n",
    "        continue\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Path to best_results.json file\n",
    "    best_results_path = os.path.join(folder_path, \"best_model_evaluation_summary.json\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Check if file exists\n",
    "    if not os.path.exists(best_results_path):\n",
            "        print(f\"⚠️ File best_model_evaluation_summary.json not found in folder: {folder_name}\")\n",
    "        continue\n",
    "    \n",
    "    try:\n",
            "        # Read JSON file\n",
    "        with open(best_results_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n",
    "            data = json.load(f)\n",
    "        \n",
            "        # Determine JSON format and extract information accordingly\n",
    "        if 'experiment_params' in data:\n",
                "            # Format 1: with experiment_params\n",
    "            experiment_info = data.get('experiment_params', {})\n",
    "            best_model_info = data.get('best_model_info', {})\n",
    "            final_metrics = data.get('final_metrics', {})\n",
    "            best_thresholds = data.get('best_thresholds', {})\n",
    "            best_values = data.get('best_values', {})\n",
    "            \n",
                "            # ROC AUC from final_metrics\n",
    "            roc_auc = final_metrics.get('roc_auc', 'N/A')\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # Try to load num_attention_heads from model config\n",
    "            model_path = find_best_model_path(folder_path)\n",
    "            num_attention_heads = 'N/A'\n",
    "            if model_path:\n",
    "                config = load_model_config(model_path)\n",
    "                if config and 'num_attention_heads' in config:\n",
    "                    num_attention_heads = config['num_attention_heads']\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # Create record for DataFrame\n",
    "            experiment_record = {\n",
    "                'folder_name': folder_name,\n",
    "                'dataset': experiment_info.get('dataset_name', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'timestamp': data.get('evaluation_timestamp', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'roc_auc': roc_auc,\n",
    "                'epochs': experiment_info.get('epochs', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'learning_rate': experiment_info.get('lr', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'batch_size': experiment_info.get('batch_size', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'eval_every': experiment_info.get('eval_every', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'seed': experiment_info.get('seed', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'dataset_strategy': experiment_info.get('dataset_strategy', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'sampling_strategy': experiment_info.get('sampling_strategy', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'positive_ratio': experiment_info.get('positive_ratio', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'use_qwen3': experiment_info.get('use_qwen3', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'total_steps': best_model_info.get('step', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'num_attention_heads': num_attention_heads,\n",
    "                'final_train_loss': 'N/A',\n",
    "                'final_test_loss': 'N/A',\n",
    "                'best_train_loss': 'N/A',\n",
    "                'best_test_loss': 'N/A'\n",
    "            }\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # Add best thresholds and values (format 1)\n",
    "            for metric in ['accuracy', 'precision', 'recall', 'f1']:\n",
    "                experiment_record[f'{metric}_threshold'] = best_thresholds.get(metric, 'N/A')\n",
    "                experiment_record[f'{metric}_value'] = best_values.get(metric, 'N/A')\n",
    "            \n",
    "        elif 'best_results' in data:\n",
    "            # Format 2: with best_results\n",
    "            best_model_info = data.get('best_model_info', {})\n",
    "            best_results = data.get('best_results', {})\n",
    "            best_thresholds = best_results.get('best_thresholds', {})\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # Parse parameters from folder name\n",
    "            experiment_info = parse_experiment_name(folder_name)\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # ROC AUC from best_results\n",
    "            roc_auc = best_results.get('roc_auc', 'N/A')\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # Try to load num_attention_heads from model config\n",
    "            model_path = find_best_model_path(folder_path)\n",
    "            num_attention_heads = 'N/A'\n",
    "            if model_path:\n",
    "                config = load_model_config(model_path)\n",
    "                if config and 'num_attention_heads' in config:\n",
    "                    num_attention_heads = config['num_attention_heads']\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # Create record for DataFrame\n",
    "            experiment_record = {\n",
    "                'folder_name': folder_name,\n",
    "                'dataset': experiment_info.get('dataset_name', 'N/A').split('_')[-1],\n",
    "                'timestamp': best_model_info.get('timestamp', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'roc_auc': roc_auc,\n",
    "                'epochs': experiment_info.get('epochs', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'learning_rate': experiment_info.get('lr', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'batch_size': experiment_info.get('batch_size', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'eval_every': experiment_info.get('eval_every', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'seed': experiment_info.get('seed', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'dataset_strategy': experiment_info.get('dataset_strategy', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'sampling_strategy': experiment_info.get('sampling_strategy', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'positive_ratio': experiment_info.get('positive_ratio', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'use_qwen3': experiment_info.get('use_qwen3', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'total_steps': best_model_info.get('step', 'N/A'),\n",
    "                'num_attention_heads': num_attention_heads,\n",
    "                'final_train_loss': 'N/A',\n",
    "                'final_test_loss': 'N/A',\n",
    "                'best_train_loss': 'N/A',\n",
    "                'best_test_loss': 'N/A'\n",
    "            }\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # Add best thresholds and values (format 2)\n",
    "            for metric in ['accuracy', 'precision', 'recall', 'f1_score']:\n",
    "                threshold_data = best_thresholds.get(metric, {})\n",
    "                if isinstance(threshold_data, dict):\n",
                        "                    # Normalize metric name\n",
    "                    metric_name = metric if metric != 'f1_score' else 'f1'\n",
    "                    experiment_record[f'{metric_name}_threshold'] = threshold_data.get('threshold', 'N/A')\n",
    "                    experiment_record[f'{metric_name}_value'] = threshold_data.get('value', 'N/A')\n",
    "        \n",
            "        else:\n",
        "            # Unknown format\n",
        "            print(f\"⚠️ Unknown JSON format in folder: {folder_name}\")\n",
    "            continue\n",
    "        \n",
    "        experiments_data.append(experiment_record)\n",
            "        # print(f\"✅ Processed folder: {folder_name}\")\n",
    "        \n",
    "    except Exception as e:\n",
            "        print(f\"❌ Error processing folder {folder_name}: {str(e)}\")\n",
    "        continue\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create DataFrame\n",
    "if experiments_data:\n",
    "    df = pd.DataFrame(experiments_data)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Sort by ROC AUC (descending)\n",
    "    df = df.sort_values('precision_value', ascending=False)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    print(f\"\\n📊 Processed experiments: {len(df)}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n🏆 Top-5 experiments by ROC AUC:\")\n",
    "    display(df[['folder_name', 'dataset', 'roc_auc', 'f1_value', 'precision_value', 'epochs', 'learning_rate', 'batch_size', 'num_attention_heads', 'use_qwen3']].head())\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Save to CSV\n",
    "    output_csv = os.path.join(results_dir, \"all_experiments_summary.csv\")\n",
    "    df.to_csv(output_csv, index=False)\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n💾 Results saved to: {output_csv}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # Show general statistics\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n📈 General statistics:\")\n",
    "    print(f\"   Average ROC AUC: {df['roc_auc'].mean():.4f}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"   Maximum ROC AUC: {df['roc_auc'].max():.4f}\")\n",
